In [21]:
#classification
results = []
names = []

for name, model in algos_Class:
    result = cross_val_score(model, X,y, cv=3, scoring='accuracy')
    names.append(name)
    results.append(result)
    
for i in range(len(names)):
    print(names[i],results[i].mean())
